<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .content {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .job-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #059669;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Application Received</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="success-icon">✅</div>

        <p>Dear {{applicantName}},</p>

        <p>Thank you for your interest in joining the Kali MHS team!</p>

        <div class="job-title">{{jobTitle}}</div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Our HR team will review your application</li>
                <li>Qualified candidates will be contacted within 7-10 business days</li>
                <li>You may be invited for an interview if your profile matches our requirements</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Application Submitted:</strong> {{submittedAt}}</p>

        <p>We appreciate the time you've taken to apply and look forward to learning more about your qualifications.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Kali MHS HR Team</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2026 Kali MHS. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>